OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday and
OL,7,FThursday with scattered heavy showers.
OL,8,FChance of overnight frost. Mostly dry
OL,9,Fand bright on Friday but a few early
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
